	"analysis":[["因为ABCD是正方形，所以AB=BC=CD=DA=2。设C的坐标为(0,0),D的坐标为(2,0),E的坐标为(1,0)。因为E是CD的中点，所以A的坐标为(-1,0)。则\overrightarrow{\mathrm{AE}}=(-1,0)-(0,0)=(-1,0), \overrightarrow{\mathrm{BD}}=(2,0)-(0,0)=(2,0). 最后计算\overrightarrow{\mathrm{AE}} \cdot \overrightarrow{\mathrm{BD}}=(-1)(2)=-2。","因为ABCD是正方形，所以AB=BC=CD=DA=2。设A的坐标为(x_{A},y_{A}),B的坐标为(x_{B},y_{B}),C的坐标为(x_{C},y_{C}),D的坐标为(x_{D},y_{D}),E的坐标为(x_{E},y_{E}).因为E是CD的中点，所以x_{E}=\frac{x_{C}+x_{D}}{2},y_{E}=\frac{y_{C}+y_{D}}{2}。因为A(x_{A},y_{A})和E(x_{E},y_{E})为点，则\overrightarrow{\mathrm{AE}}=\langle x_{A}-x_{E},y_{A}-y_{E}\rangle。同理因为B(x_{B},y_{B})和D(x_{D},y_{D})为点，则\overrightarrow{\mathrm{BD}}=\langle x_{B}-x_{D},y_{B}-y_{D}\rangle。则\overrightarrow{\mathrm{AE}} \cdot \overrightarrow{\mathrm{BD}}=(x_{A}-x_{E})(x_{B}-x_{D})+(y_{A}-y_{E})(y_{B}-y_{D})。因为ABCD是正方形，所以x_{A}=x_{D},y_{A}=y_{D},x_{B}=x_{C},y_{B}=y_{C}。所以\overrightarrow{\mathrm{AE}} \cdot \overrightarrow{\mathrm{BD}}=(x_{A}-x_{C})(x_{A}-x_{D})+(y_{A}-y_{C})(y_{A}-y_{D})=(x_{A}-x_{C})^{2}+(y_{A}-y_{C})^{2}=2^{2}+2^{2}=8."]],
