	"analysis":[["当 x=-x 时，f(x)=f(-x)，即 x \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)=-x \ln \left(-x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)。因此，我们有 \begin{align*} x \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) &amp;= -x \ln \left(-x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) &amp;= -\ln \left(-x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) &amp;= \ln \left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}-x}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= \frac{1}{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}-x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+2x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+a+x^{2} &amp;= 1 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x^{2}+2x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+a &amp;= 1 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2x^{2}+2x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+a &amp;= 1 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2x^{2}+2x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+a-1 &amp;= 0 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+\frac{a-1}{2} &amp;= 0 \end{align*} 令 x=-x 时，f(x)=f(-x)。因此，我们有 \begin{align*} (-x)^{2}+(-x)\sqrt{a+(-x)^{2}}+\frac{a-1}{2} &amp;= 0 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}-x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+\frac{a-1}{2} &amp;= 0 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+\frac{a-1}{2} &amp;= 0 \\ \end{align*} 因为 x^{2}+x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+\frac{a-1}{2} = 0 和 x^{2}+x\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+\frac{a-1}{2} = 0，唯一的解是 a = 1。","解法一：因为函数 f(x) 为偶函数，所以 f(-x) = f(x)。因此，我们有 \begin{align*} f(-x) &amp;= f(x) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad (-x) \ln \left((-x) + \sqrt{a + (-x)^{2}}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(x + \sqrt{a + x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \left(x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(x + \sqrt{a + x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}\right)^{-1} &amp;= \ln \left(x + \sqrt{a + x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\frac{1}{x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}}\right) &amp;= \ln \left(x + \sqrt{a + x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \frac{1}{x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}} &amp;= x + \sqrt{a + x^{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \frac{1}{x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}} (x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}) &amp;= (x + \sqrt{a + x^{2}}) (x - \sqrt{a + x^{2}}) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 1 &amp;= x^{2} - (a + x^{2}) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 1 &amp;= x^{2} - a - x^{2} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 1 &amp;= -a \\ \Rightarrow\qquad a &amp;= -1 \end{align*} ","解法二：因为 f(-x)=f(x)，所以 (-x) \ln \left((-x)+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)=x \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)。因此，我们有 \begin{align*} (-x) \ln \left((-x)+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left((-x)+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)^{-x} &amp;= \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\frac{1}{(-x)+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}\right)^{-x} &amp;= \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad (-x) \ln \left(\frac{1}{(-x)+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(x+\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}-x}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}-x\right)^{-1} &amp;= x \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}-x}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\frac{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}-x}{1}\right)^{-x} &amp;= \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\frac{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}{x+1}\right)^{-x} &amp;= \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\frac{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}{x+1}\right)^{-x} &amp;= \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \left(\frac{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}{x+1}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} + x \ln (x+1) &amp;= x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} + x \ln x \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} + x \ln (x+1) &amp;= x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} + x \ln x \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} - x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x \ln x + x \ln (x+1) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -2x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x(\ln x + \ln (x+1)) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -2x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x \ln (x(x+1)) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -2x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x \ln (x^{2}+x) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -2x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x \ln (x(x+1)) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad -2x \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x \ln (x^{2}+x) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad (-2x) \ln \sqrt{a+x^{2}} &amp;= x \ln (x^{2}+x) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right)^{-2x} &amp;= \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}\right)^{-2x} &amp;= \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad (-2x) \ln \left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{a+x^{2}}}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2x \ln \left(\sqrt{a+x^{2}}\right) &amp;= x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{1}{x}} &amp;= x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{1}{x}} &amp;= x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{1}{x}} &amp;= x \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2 \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{x}{x}} &amp;= \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2 \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right) &amp;= \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{2} &amp;= \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{2} &amp;= \ln \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad 2 \log(x^{2}+x) &amp;= x \log(x^{2}+x) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \log(x^{2}+x) &amp;= \frac{x}{2} \log(x^{2}+x) \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \log(x^{2}+x) &amp;= \log(x^{2}+x)^{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \log(x^{2}+x) &amp;= \log(x^{2}+x)^{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x &amp;= (x^{2}+x)^{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x &amp;= (x^{2}+x)^{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{2}{2}} &amp;= \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{1} &amp;= \left(x^{2}+x\right)^{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \frac{x^{2}+x}{1} &amp;= \frac{x^{2}+x}{\frac{x}{2}} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \frac{x^{2}+x}{1} &amp;= \frac{2x^{2}+2x}{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x &amp;= \frac{2x^{2}+2x}{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x &amp;= \frac{2x(x+1)}{x} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x &amp;= 2x+2 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}+x-2x-2 &amp;= 0 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}-2x-2 &amp;= 0 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x^{2}-2x &amp;= 2 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \left(x^{2}-2x+1\right) &amp;= 2+1 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \left(x-1\right)^{2} &amp;= 3 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad \left(x-1\right)^{2} &amp;= 3 \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x-1 &amp;= \sqrt{3} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x &amp;= 1+\sqrt{3} \\ \Rightarrow\qquad x &amp;= \sqrt{3}+1 \\ \end{align*} 最终结果是1

